I'll be right back.

45
00:04:15,701 --> 00:04:16,869
They're dead.

46
00:04:19,830 --> 00:04:22,290
GIRL 1: Don't reply yet.
GIRL 2: Yes, I have to reply.

47
00:04:22,374 --> 00:04:24,417
-That's not…
