fallen, nobody would've gotten killed.

62
00:04:55,825 --> 00:04:56,868
JANE: Ouch.

63
00:04:57,076 --> 00:05:00,581
-ZIGGY: Did you hurt yourself?
-No, the lady just tripped.

64
00:05:05,669 --> 00:05:06,670
