00:38:49,046 --> 00:38:51,965
That's what you get if you go down
to the beach without me or your mom.

721
00:38:52,049 --> 00:38:53,550
-MAX: But…
-Strictly forbidden.

722
00:38:53,634 --> 00:38:54,885
