843
00:46:23,681 --> 00:46:25,141
<i>It's the sow.</i>

844
00:46:26,434 --> 00:46:28,644
GIBSON: <i>Tell me about Celeste Wright.</i>

845
00:46:29,312 --> 00:46:30,604
GABRIELLE: [SCOFFS]
<i>Something had to be wrong.</i>

846
00:46:30,688 --> 00:46:32,941
JACKIE: <i>So elegant, so…</i>
MADELINE: <i>Volcanic.</i>

847
00:46:33,108 --> 00:46:34,359
Madeline Mackenzie?

848
00:46:34,485 --> 00:46:35,568
Things never blow over…

849
00:46:35,652 --> 00:46:37,154
<i>Once Madeline gets involved.</i>

850
00:46:37,321 --> 00:46:38,780
<i>They blow up.</i>

851
